  "texts": [
    "After querying the meta-toxic knowledge graph, the ultimate toxicity knowledge is retrieved as supplementary information.",
    "We then insert the retrieved knowledge into the prompt template utilized for enhancing LLM's ability to detect hatred and toxicity.",
    "Two exemplars are designed to inform the LLM on utilizing external toxicity knowledge.",
    "The prompting template is presented in Appendix A.5.",
    "As outlined in Section 3.1, we construct three meta-toxic knowledge graphs based on the HateXplain, ToxicSpans, and IHC datasets, respectively, with Qwen2.5-14B-Instruct (Qwen) (Qwen Team, 2024)."
